'''''Anney Anney''''' (English: ''Brother Brother'') is a [[1983 in film|1983]] [[Tamil language|Tamil]] [[Cinema of India|Indian]] [[feature film]] [[Film director|directed]] by [[Mouli (Director)|Mouli]] for Kalaivani. The film stars [[Mouli (Director)|Mouli]], [[Viji]] and [[Sumithra (actress)|Sumithra]] in the lead roles.<ref>{{cite web|title=Anney Anney LP Vinyl Records|url=http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers/84/3/1/1|publisher=musicalaya|accessdate=2014-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140425003738/http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers%2F84%2F3%2F1%2F1|archive-date=25 April 2014|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>http://spicyonion.com/movie/anney-anney/</ref> the movie was average at  the box office

